    "This section demonstrates the practical applicability of our proposed latent-free Vecchia approximation for Bayesian spatially varying coefficients models with censored data.",
    "The case study analyze hydrocarbon contamination data from the Toulouse Metropolis, France.",
    "It represents a typical environmental monitoring scenario where detection limits create substantial censoring challenges, and spatial heterogeneity necessitates flexible modeling approaches.",
